::DarkMouse::
She looked at him for a moment.  She didn't quite understand what he was 
hinting at.  She knew he was hinting at something, but what it was, she 
didn't know.
"Well commander, I don't know. I shall do what ever my commander asks of me. 
  What do you want to do?"
She felt silly.  She had no experience in matters as these.  She had seen 
the other bots flirt. But didn't know what to do after that. This was just 
something beyond her programming.  She blushed and couldn't stop.  She felt 
bad because she wanted to make her commander happy. But beyond a kiss, her 
programming was incomplete.

Scorponok smiled at Darkmouse. He looked at her and Said. "Well, umm,
the Lab is Finish, So what do you want to do. Stay in her or go do
something else?" He walked up to her and looked straight into her
eyes, "So what do you want to do, Beautiful?"
